# Card

A `sl-card` component is a simple rounded box that contains various other components.

<Preview>
  <sl-card>
    <span>Card Title</span>
  </sl-card>
</Preview>

``` html
<sl-card>
  <span>Card Title</span>
</sl-card>
```

## Slots

The component includes multiple slots to cover various layouts.

<Preview title="Variants" class="slots">
  <div class="content">
    <sl-card>
      {#if showHeaderSlot}
        <span slot="header">Header Slot</span>
      {/if}
      {#if showDefaultSlot}
        <span>Default Slot</span>
      {/if}
      {#if showFooterSlot}
        <span slot="footer">Footer Slot</span>
      {/if}
    </sl-card>
  </div>
  <sl-form>
    <sl-form-control label="Header">
      <sl-input-checkbox value={showHeaderSlot} on:update={({ detail }) => { showHeaderSlot = detail; }}/>
    </sl-form-control>
    <sl-form-control label="Default">
      <sl-input-checkbox value={showDefaultSlot} on:update={({ detail }) => { showDefaultSlot = detail; }}/>
    </sl-form-control>
    <sl-form-control label="Footer">
      <sl-input-checkbox value={showFooterSlot} on:update={({ detail }) => { showFooterSlot = detail; }}/>
    </sl-form-control>
  </sl-form>
</Preview>

``` html
<sl-card>
  <span slot="header">Header Slot</span>  
  <span>Default Slot</span>
  <span slot="footer">Footer Slot</span>  
</sl-card>
```

